Trade/Device Name(s): VITROS Chemistry Products AAT/HPT Performance Verifier I, II, and III
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for VITROS Chemistry Products Calibrator Kit 99 and AAT/HPT Performance Verifier I, II, and III for quantitative measurement and performance monitoring of proteins using VITROS 5,1 FS Chemistry Systems.
Indications for Use Summary: Used to calibrate and monitor performance of protein measurements in body fluids on VITROS 5,1 FS Chemistry Systems for in vitro diagnostic use.
